+  // Raven descriptor (Plan 03): when a fingerprint profile is active, deny
+  // geolocation outright. The descriptor carries no coordinate field yet, so
+  // returning any real position would leak the true device location. Report
+  // PERMISSION_DENIED through the same fatal-error path used by the
+  // insecure-origin and permissions-policy denials below, and skip querying
+  // the real device entirely.
